<div class="nbunit" id="8Nov1933"><font color="red">8 November 1933</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): Servire Press &hellip; say .. most suitable time for them would be to publish between April 1st and May 31st. </div>
